('', 'Baine! Thank the Light you\'re alive!', 201485, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 165121, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 36949),
('', 'We must concentrate. The Purpose will be fulfilled.', 201477, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 160688, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 36949),
