('', 'The stone responds to you, $n! Try to activate it while we hold off the Jailer\'s army!', 197752, 0, 0, 5, 0, 0, 0, 163168, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 36949),
('Death comes for the soul of your world! All that you see--all that you know--will be undone!', '', 197748, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 163195, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 36949),
('', 'It\'s nearly charged! Do not falter!', 197747, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 163166, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 36949),
