('So the stones crumble under your might. This will not be forgotten.', '', 197713, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 164679, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 36949),
('Denathrius\'s elite forces hold this ward, and will strike at us from here unless routed.', '', 197712, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 164678, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 36949),
