('', 'It is not yet your time, child of Azeroth.', 197665, 0, 0, 457, 0, 0, 0, 167120, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 36949),
('', 'With defeat, comes wisdom.', 197664, 0, 0, 457, 0, 0, 0, 167119, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 36949),
