('', 'Next time your ally will stay your demise, I am certain.', 197662, 0, 0, 457, 0, 0, 0, 167117, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 36949),
('', 'You will do better next time.', 197661, 0, 0, 457, 0, 0, 0, 167116, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 36949),
