('Lord Admiral, before we found you, did you see any sign of the Night Warrior?', '', 195289, 0, 0, 6, 0, 0, 161966, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 36949),
('Another ambush! Bring them down!', '', 195287, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 161965, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 36949),
('What did Thrall mean by \"slip past them again\"? You\'ve escaped before?', '', 195285, 0, 0, 6, 0, 0, 161962, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 36949),
('', 'So much for remaining unnoticed. Let\'s hurry.', 195284, 0, 0, 5, 0, 0, 0, 161961, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 36949),
('Knights, secure the cave! We\'ll hold off these fiends.', '', 195282, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 161960, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 36949),
('', 'There\'s a cave just around the bend. With any luck, we can reach it before they notice.', 195279, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 161957, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 36949),
('', 'The illusion won\'t hold for long. Hurry!', 195278, 0, 0, 5, 0, 0, 0, 161956, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 36949),
('', 'I left some mirror images behind to keep them distracted.', 195277, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 161955, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 36949),
('', 'They\'ve found us! Be ready!', 195276, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 161953, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 36949),
('Something\'s flying at us from above!', '', 195275, 0, 0, 22, 0, 0, 161952, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 36949),
('Thank you for coming to my aid, Jaina.', '', 195274, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 161951, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 36949),
('I... will manage.', '', 195273, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 161950, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 36949),
('', 'We can\'t stay here. Can you walk, Thrall?', 195272, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 161949, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 36949),
('Keep an eye out for clues that point to the whereabouts of our allies.', '', 195270, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 161931, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 36949),
('We are vastly outnumbered. Let\'s try not to draw unwanted attention.', '', 195269, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 161930, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 36949),
('Let\'s get moving--before reinforcements arrive.', '', 195266, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 161929, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 36949),
('We have done all we can here.', '', 195265, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 161928, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 36949),
