('That one was my favorite!', '', 193274, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 154583, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 36949),
('', 'Sentries from the House of Rituals keep this area under observation. They will find no secrets here. Destroy them.', 193273, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 153890, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 36949),
