('Bring me the supplies. I\'ll show you how to make a trap with them.', '', 191037, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 152922, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 36949),
('', 'An ice mote? Sure. What\'re ye gonna do with it?', 191035, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 152941, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 36949),
('', 'Ye got two foes attackin\' ye now. Cast Polymorph tae even the odds!', 191031, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 152948, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 36949),
('', 'I didn\'t! $p did.', 191030, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 152952, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 36949),
