('', 'Yer polymorphed foe will wander around fer a bit. Use that tae yer advantage and fight whoever\'s left.', 191027, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 152950, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 36949),
('', 'Very funny, recruit. I think ye got the hang of this. Let\'s go back.', 191025, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 152949, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 36949),
