('We saved Meredy, all thanks to $n!', '', 178875, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 153037, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 36949),
('The captain will be thrilled! Let\'s get back to camp and deliver the good news.', '', 178864, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 153036, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 36949),
('', 'She will be. Come on!', 178862, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 152963, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 36949),
('Let\'s deal with those harpies. I just hope Meredy is okay...', '', 178861, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 153033, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 36949),
